<p>Yosemite is a new OS, and with that comes oddities. Thankfully your two favorite geeks are here to help. Mail issues are plaguing many listeners and John F. Braun and Dave Hamilton talk you through how to keep things running as clean as possible, even cleaning up Mail behind the scenes. Then it&#39;s on to custom FaceTime ringtones, how to manage the battery on a spare iPhone and much, much more. Download today and enjoy!</p>
